items.title: NYC Mayor Zohran Mamdani inaugurated, addresses New Yorkers

items.title: Fire kills dozens at crowded Swiss Alps bar on New Year's
items.description: Police in Switzerland say a fire at a bar in the Crans-Montana ski resort area is believed to have left about 40 people dead and dozens more injured.

items.title: Trump says he underwent CT scan, not MRI, during October examination
